Package org.framed.orm.ui.command.connectionkinds

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CallRelationshipConstraintsActionCommand
    Through this command the RelationshipConstraintsAction is called.
    ORMRelationCreateBendpointCommand
    With this command a Bendpoint for Relation can be created.
    ORMRelationCreateCommand
    Through this command all Relations can be created(invoked into the model tree).
    ORMRelationDeleteBendpointCommand
    Command used to delete/remove a Bendpoint.
    ORMRelationDeleteCommand
    Through this command all Relations except the Relations from type cyclic, total, acyclic, reflexive and irreflexive(relationshipConstraints) can be deleted(removed from the model tree).
    ORMRelationMoveBendpointCommand
    Through this command a Bendpoint can be moved frome an old position to a new one.
    ORMRelationshipConstraintCreateCommand
    Through this command Relations from type cyclic, total, acyclic, reflexive and irreflexive can be created(invoked into the model tree).
    ORMRelationshipConstraintDeleteCommand
    Through this command Relations from type total, cyclic and irreflexive can be deleted(removed from the model tree).
